snippet.title: Draft Day Sports: College Football 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the ultimate in college football gaming. Take control of your favorite school and make the decisions that can build your school into a dynasty and you into a coaching legend.

This year's version offers more customization like a 16 team playoff option, more strategy options, new recruiting periods for the increased transfers, a new in game trophy room and so much more.

Try a free demo today at https://www.wolverinestudios.com
